# Per-package lockfiles: this is an npm-workspaces monorepo, so the ROOT
# package-lock.json is the only authoritative lock. A stray lock committed
# inside a workspace (a leftover `npm install` in a package dir) desyncs
# Dependabot and CI — see the khai-methods fossil that produced a phantom
# advisory and a downgrade PR. Ignore nested locks; never the root one.
packages/**/package-lock.json
